Package ch.vehicles.tbz.vehicles

Class Vehicle

  • java.lang.Object
    • ch.vehicles.tbz.vehicles.Vehicle
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Definable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ElectroCar, MotorizedVehicle
    public abstract class Vehicle
extends java.lang.Object
implements Definable
    This class is an entity which represents a vehicle and contains all the needed data, to define it. Every other vehicle class extends from this one. Its the root class.
